XSpaceGrow - Device Activation Instructions
===========================================

Hi <%= @user.display_name || @user.email.split('@').first.capitalize %>,

Your <%= @device_name %> is ready to be activated and connected to your XSpaceGrow dashboard!

YOUR ACTIVATION TOKEN
=====================
<%= @token %>

IMPORTANT: This token expires on <%= @expires_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %>

ACTIVATION STEPS
================

1. POWER ON YOUR DEVICE
   Connect your <%= @device_name %> to power and ensure it's within range of your WiFi network.

2. ENTER ACTIVATION TOKEN
   Use the device interface or web portal to enter your activation token:
   <%= @token %>

3. CONFIGURE WIFI
   Follow the on-device prompts to connect to your WiFi network and complete the setup.

4. MONITOR YOUR DEVICE
   Once activated, your device will appear in your XSpaceGrow dashboard for monitoring and control.

